<span id="freeTextContainer13253495864429079041">This book is beautifully written.<br/>I have a recently diagnosed child with Aspergers and whilst I’m familiarising myself with the term, he is just as I’ve always known him. <br/>This book felt so familiar to me as I recognised so many traits in Caitlin that I see in my son. It is hard not to be drawn emotionally into this story, and I loved every page.<br/>Wonderful stuff and easily 4 stars ⭐️ </span>

